<div class = "col-xs-3"></div>
	<div class = "col-xs-6">
		<div class="jumbotron center ">
			<h1>Lets Groog up!</h1>
			<% if user_signed_in? %>
			  <%= link_to "Create a new group!", new_group_path, class: "btn btn-primary btn-lg" %>
			<% else %>
			  <%= link_to "Log in", new_user_session_path, class: "btn btn-default btn-lg" %>
			  <%= link_to "Sign up", new_user_registration_path, class: "btn btn-primary btn-lg" %>
			<% end%> 
		</div>
	</div>
</div>
<br>
<div class="container">
	<div class="row clearfix">
		<div class="col-md-12 column">
	<div class="jumbotron center ">
		<div class="row clearfix">
			<div class="col-md-6 column">
				<h3>Create Group</h3>
				<p>
					Creating a group could not be easier. Simply name the group with a discription
					and your on your way. A URL will be generated that links to your group so you can further
					invite others to join.
				</p>
			</div>
			<div class="col-md-6 column">
				<%= image_tag "new_group.png" %>
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="row clearfix">
			<div class="col-md-6 column">
				<%= image_tag "group_active.png" %>
			</div>
			<div class="col-md-6 column">
				<h3>Active Groups</h3>
				<p class="text-left">
					Are you overwhelmed keeping up with multiple groups you are appart of? Well with Groog
					you can manage and switch between groups as simple as two clicks.
				</p>
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="row clearfix">
			<div class="col-md-6 column">
				<h3>Chat</h3>
				<p>
					You cant have a group without actuaully communicating with them. So this top of the line next gen chat system will help you do just that.
				</p>
			</div>
			<div class="col-md-6 column">
				<%= image_tag "chat.png" %>
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="row clearfix">
			<div class="col-md-6 column">
				<%= image_tag "tasks.png" %>
			</div>
			<div class="col-md-6 column">
				<h3>Assign Tasks</h3>
				<p class="text-left">
					Feeling like your teamates are lost and need a sense of direction? Well how about assigning them a task to help them move foward. Want to know the best part? You can even assing a due date. BAM!
				</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>



